==Information==
It has been announced that {{ShipLink|Murasame/Kai|text=Murasame}} and {{ShipLink|Tatsuta}} will both be receiving Kai Ni Remodels this month January.
===Hints given towards Murasame Kai Ni===
*Is a Shiratsuyu-class Destroyer
*'''Went through the Battle of Solomon Seas and etc.'''
*'''Flagship of 4th Torpedo Squadron'''
**Murasame is known to having become the Flagship of the 4th Torpedo Squadron after Yura had sunk during the Guadalcanal Campaign and with Nagara having retreating back to Japan.

===Tatsuta Kai Ni===
*Old Model Light Cruiser
*Went through Transport Operations and Supported in Frontlines as well.
*Had Exceeding Performance by World Standards during its Launch during the time.
*Confirmed via Twitter Avatar Teaser

